title: Fountain Vegetarian Restaurant
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Chinese, International, Take-out, Catering, Banquet
description: The extensive all vegetarian menu features yum cha, main entrees with faux meats, hot pots, cakes and desserts, coffee, teas, non-alcoholic beverages, and more. Fine bamboo interior with soothing music, a relaxing atmosphere in front of the Bella Vista Water Fountain.
